{
  "chapter": 89,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十九回\"胜败\"讲述李寻欢与上官金虹终极对决的结果。阿飞与孙小红在门外焦急等待，孙小红劝阿飞离开，阿飞拒绝，表示要为李寻欢报仇。李寻欢最终活着走出房门，他解释上官金虹因想赌一赌能否躲过小李飞刀而故意错过多次杀他的机会，最终败亡。阿飞进入房间看到上官金虹的尸体和荆无命。荆无命因主人之死形同空壳，阿飞与他交手后选择不杀他，以\"以牙还牙\"的方式给了荆无命最后一次机会，正如当初荆无命给他机会一样。本章展现了李寻欢\"爱比恨更有力量\"的人格魅力，以及阿飞从仇恨走向宽恕的成长。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你快走吧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你……你叫我走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你非走不可，我……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我跟你不同。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我早就说过，他死了，我也不能独活，可是你……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我并不想陪他死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么你就该走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我也不想走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你应该知道我是为了什么。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我知道你一定要为他报仇，但那也用不着急在一时，你可以等……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我不能等。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "不能等就……就……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "就怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "就死！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我也知道你一定还想试试，但那也没有用的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你留在这里陪他死又有什么用？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你留下来，只因有件事你纵然明知做了没有用，还是非做不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你说话的口气越来越像他了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官金虹若知道我们就在这里等着，一定开心得很。",
      "tone": "凄然",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "就让他开心吧，这世上本就只有好人才痛苦，开心的本就是恶人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你错了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你错了，这世上的好人是永远不会寂寞的，恶人痛苦的时候也永远要比开心的时候多得多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上官金虹呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "想必也很痛苦，因为他毕竟还是做错了一件事！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他做错了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他的确有很多机会能杀我，他甚至可以令我根本无法还手，可是他却故意将机会错过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "因为他心里始终想赌一赌。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "赌？赌什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "赌他自己是不是能躲得过我的出手一刀。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他当然不信'小李飞刀，例不虚发'这句话的。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他不信——任何人他都不信，这世上根本没有一件能让他相信的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "结果呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他输了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你不想复仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你不敢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你腰上既然还有剑，为何不敢抽出来？难道你的剑只是摆摆样子的么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你还是很快，但不能杀人了，你可知道这是为了什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "这只因你比别人更想死，当然就杀不了别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我却能杀你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "但我不杀你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你不杀我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "我不杀你，只因你是荆无命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你可以走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你给了我一次机会，我也给你一次……最后一次。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要杀一个人很容易，但若要他好好地活着，就难得多了。",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "世上武功最高的两个人已被你们击败了，天下势力最大的一个帮会也已在你们手中瓦解，你们本该觉得很开心、很得意才对，但你们看起来却连一点高兴的样子都没有，简直就好像败的是你们自己一样。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 89,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 369
    }
  ],
